  "instructions": "<p>Great spawn for paladins level 250+ for both experience and loot.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>It's a place to hunt in area, luring a few monsters and shooting avalanches + <em>exevo mas san</em>.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>Start by luring 3~4 monsters, feeling the respawn, understanding how many monsters you can block and closing half a box. As you feel more confident you can lure more monsters and even close a full box (8 monsters).</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>üõ°Ô∏è Recommended equipments:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Amulet: Sleep Shawl, Magma Amulet or Dragon Necklace.</li>\n  <li>Ring: Prismatic Ring, Blister Ring or Ring of Blue Plasma.</li>\n  <li>Helmet: Zaoan Helmet.</li>\n  <li>Armor: Depth Lorica.</li>\n  <li>Legs: Fabulous Legs or Prismatic Legs.</li>\n  <li>Boots: Guardian Boots.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>‚ö°Ô∏è Imbuements:</p>\n<p>It's mandatory and without it you may not be able to hunt.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>1x Powerful Critical Hit.</li>\n  <li>2x Powerful Life Leech.</li>\n  <li>2x Powerful Mana Leech.</li>\n  <li>1x Powerful Dragon Hide (optional).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>‚öóÔ∏è Charm runes:</p>\n<p>It's not required but will help a lot if you have.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Dodge or Wound on Draken Spellweaver.</li>\n  <li>Freeze on Draken Warmaster.</li>\n</ul>",
